title: The Strange Case of Dr. Manning

sources.title: The Strange Case of Dr. Manning
sources.description: Title: The Strange Case of Dr. Manning Summary: Directed by: Arthur Crabtree Actors: Greta Gynt, Ron Randell, Garard Green Production Company: Republic Pictures (I) Release Date: 21 March 1958 (USA) Aspect Ratio: 1.85 : 1 Add Full Plot

metadata.Plot: Dr. Manning, husband of a wealthy socialite, is kidnapped while making a late night housecall. Insurance investigator Logan is called and the hunt is on for kidnapped and kidnapper.
metadata.Writer: Bill Luckwell, Paul Tabori, Leo Townsend
metadata.Actors: Greta Gynt, Ron Randell, Garard Green
